claims:
1. the accumulator electric ship of a wind/light energy, the charging of bank electricity, comprise catamaran hull (1), it is characterized in that: electric propulsion apparatus (4) is connected 5 with storage battery (3) with battery charger respectively by compound type central control desk (2)) be connected, battery charger (5) is provided with bank electricity access device;
      Also be provided with aerogenerator (6) and solar panel (7) on catamaran hull (1), aerogenerator (6) is connected with compound type central control desk (2) by wind/light energy power generation control (11) with solar panel (7), and is connected with storage battery (3) by compound type central control desk (2);
      The square wave permanent magnetic brushless direct current motor that the phase decoupling type direct current frequency-variable stepless speed regulation controller that the PWM technology that in electric propulsion apparatus (4), employing can adopt the regenerative brake mode to reclaim braking kinetic energy is controlled drives;
      Storage battery (3) adopts the LiFePO4 power accumulator of quickly-chargeable;
      Place in the battery flat of storage battery (3) a plurality of temperature control apparatuss (13) are installed, temperature control apparatus (13) is connected with the accumulator room room temperature centralized control read out instrument (12) of compound type central control desk (2) inside by cable;
      Described temperature control apparatus (13) is comprised of temperature sensor, minitype motivation radiator and ventilator tube, be distributed in the storage battery cabin everywhere with dot matrix way, wherein have at least a temperature control apparatus (13) to be located at battery flat and install between the cabin of electric propulsion apparatus (4), be used for promoting the temperature of battery flat, be controlled in 40-70 ℃ of scope by the temperature of temperature control apparatus (13) with battery flat.
